data.description: Welcome to this spacious corner lot home located in The Trails subdivision, just 15 miles away from Kirtland AFB. The home contains 4 bedrooms & 3 bathrooms, office space and loft upstairs providing plenty of space & privacy. The master suite is complete with a private balcony offering mountain views. Step outside to discover the backyard, an entertainer's dream. The large deck, turf, fire pit & pergola offer an excellent space for entertaining. Additional features of this home include an outdoor storage shed, a laundry area conveniently located upstairs near the master bedroom, and all appliances - including washer and dryer - are included, making this home truly move-in ready.
